snippet.title: Shadow The Hedgehog Reloaded Release 1.0 - Mod Info & Download
snippet.description:
Download here:
https://github.com/ShadowTheHedgehogHacking/ShdTH-Reloaded/releases

Setup video here if needed:
https://youtu.be/uv9gpqEbXU4

If you want Japanese voices:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5eqV0ded5ts

Director/Main Hacker's (LimblessVector's Channel)
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRxAsMP4Sc38303lwuDQIAA


Credits for Songs Used:
Angry Hyena - INGODWEROCK (Original) - Metalstep
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yzruBMg8bW8

Streets of Seoul - INGODWEROCK
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=03USeAGFs-0

Subscribe to the music author:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCahkUTjtwdZb125AbXHIzCg




Fun fact if you're down here, the earliest non-proto build of Shadow we have is the USA GameCube Version. It was built on Oct 10, 2005. 17 years later Reloaded 1.0 comes out the same day.
